      "writtenOn": "2018-07-13T22:44:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Should this become a fatal error? I think it can happen only if someone messes with the manifest file manually (so contents of the manifest !\u003d what\u0027s in the package file). I kept it as a warning, since I believe even if it happens, RepairDeployed makes enough progress to be useful.",
